author: Sam Meads | smeads@mlive.com
title: Masyn Shannon and Alize Tripp lead Michigan Center to district semi win over Concord
text: Michigan Center received two standout performances in a 66-49 district semifinal win over Concord on Wednesday. Masyn Shannon led the Cardinals with 27 points, and Alize Tripp scored 21. Michigan Center coach Joe Lusk said Shannon got in foul trouble...
